#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.float_power.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.float\\_power"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:1 of
msgid "First tensor elements raised to powers from second array, element-wise."
msgstr "第一个张量的元素逐元素地提升为第二个数组中对应的幂。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:3 of
msgid ""
"Raise each base in `x1` to the positionally-corresponding power in `x2`. "
"`x1` and `x2` must be broadcastable to the same shape. This differs from "
"the power function in that integers, float16, and float32  are promoted "
"to floats with a minimum precision of float64 so that the result is "
"always inexact.  The intent is that the function will return a usable "
"result for negative powers and seldom overflow for positive powers."
msgstr ""
"将 `x1` 中的每个底数提升为 `x2` 中位置对应的幂。`x1` 和 `x2` 必须可以广播"
"到相同的形状。这与幂函数不同的是，整数、float16 和 float32 会被提升为至少"
" float64 精度的浮点数，因此结果总是不精确的。此函数的目的是对负幂返回可用"
"的结果，并且很少在正幂时发生溢出。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:10 of
msgid "The bases."
msgstr "底数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:12 of
msgid "The exponents."
msgstr "指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:14 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:19 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:24 of
msgid "**y** -- The bases in `x1` raised to the exponents in `x2`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x1` 中的底数被提升为 `x2` 中的指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`power`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:30 of
msgid "power function that preserves type"
msgstr "保留类型的幂函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:34 of
msgid "Cube each element in a list."
msgstr "对列表中的每个元素求立方。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:44 of
msgid "Raise the bases to different exponents."
msgstr "将底数提升为不同的指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.float_power.float_power:50 of
msgid "The effect of broadcasting."
msgstr "广播的效果。"

